1
00:00:09,085 --> 00:00:12,440
Oi! Take the [SOMETHING], something to drink!

2
00:00:13,090 --> 00:00:14,177
Don't drink that!

3
00:00:14,440 --> 00:00:15,262
Why not?

4
00:00:15,668 --> 00:00:18,377
Cuz, uh... If brew is made by Glukkons,

5
00:00:18,377 --> 00:00:20,370
it's probably bad for you.

6
00:00:21,017 --> 00:00:22,114
<i>What a wuss!</i>

7
00:00:22,331 --> 00:00:23,274
I hear ya.

8
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,182
Look Abe,

9
00:00:24,497 --> 00:00:27,982
we came all this way, just to help you.

10
00:00:28,045 --> 00:00:28,445
Well but-

11
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:33,051
It's not unreasonable, that we are just a little bit thirsty.

12
00:00:33,285 --> 00:00:33,817
Now is it?

13
00:00:33,845 --> 00:00:34,240
Yeah, but-

14
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:37,588
In case you didn't notice, we just walked across a desert.

15
00:00:37,860 --> 00:00:39,817
So back off, Stich-Lips.

16
00:00:40,045 --> 00:00:42,131
But... D'ohhh!

17
00:00:48,342 --> 00:00:49,880
I tried to stop them.

18
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,685
But they drank the brew anyway.

19
00:00:57,542 --> 00:00:58,588
Lot's of it...

20
00:00:59,697 --> 00:01:01,462
Then they got all sick looking.

21
00:01:01,868 --> 00:01:03,737
But they still wanted more!

22
00:01:07,365 --> 00:01:09,948
That's when I figured this whole thing out.

23
00:01:10,588 --> 00:01:12,868
Brew was made from our bones!

24
00:01:13,091 --> 00:01:15,731
This is bad, what do I do now?

25
00:01:16,017 --> 00:01:20,348
What do you do? How about leading us outta here?

26
00:01:22,062 --> 00:01:24,005
Uh, ok. Follow me!

27
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,051
Okay...

28
00:01:25,988 --> 00:01:26,205
But!

29
00:01:26,308 --> 00:01:28,325
[Screaming]

30
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,514
Oops, I forgot he was blind!

31
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,228
Help the rescue the rest of them!

32
00:01:37,977 --> 00:01:39,417
I can't believe it!

33
00:01:39,805 --> 00:01:42,257
That's him, it's that Abe guy!

34
00:01:42,874 --> 00:01:44,982
Promotion, here I come!

35
00:01:45,251 --> 00:01:45,954
Freeze!

